              <p>ADHD Advisor uses flat pricing &mdash; $199 total, shown before you book &mdash; instead of in-network billing, so your price never depends on a plan, a deductible, or a network. HSA and FSA funds are accepted, and a superbill is provided for possible out-of-network reimbursement. Talkiatry works the opposite way: in-network only, around $30 per visit on most plans per their site.</p>
